// MARK: - Welcome to Planet
"Welcome to Planet" = "歡迎來到 Planet";
"Build and publish and follow websites on IPFS" = "在 IPFS 上建置、發佈和關注網站";
"Manage multiple IPNS ready to be linked to your ENS" = "管理多個可關聯到 ENS 的 IPNS";
"Two-column Markdown editor for writing and previewing" = "用於撰寫和預覽的雙欄 Markdown 編輯器";
"Export and import websites between Macs" = "在多台 Mac 之間匯出和匯入網站";

"Continue" = "繼續";

"Mark All as Read" = "全部標示為已讀";
"Unfollow" = "取消關注";

"Do you want to save your changes as a draft?" = "要將變更儲存為草稿嗎？";

"Are you sure you want to unfollow this planet?" = "確定要取消關注這個 Planet 嗎？";

"Here are your archived Planets. Archived planets are not auto published or updated. You can unarchive them from here." = "這些是你已封存的網站。已封存的網站不會自動發佈或更新。你可以在這裡取消封存。";


"Are you sure you want to delete %@? This action cannot be undone." = "確定要刪除 %@ 嗎？此操作無法還原。";

"Are you sure you want to delete this post?\n\n%@?\n\nThis action cannot be undone." = "確定要刪除這篇貼文嗎？\n\n%@\n\n此操作無法還原。";

"Would you like to use new library location at" = "是否要使用新的資料庫位置：";

"current database including following planets will be replaced with contents at this location" = "目前資料庫（包括關注的網站）將由此位置中的內容取代。";

"When you tip a creator, transactions will be sent to the selected Ethereum network." = "打賞創作者時，交易會傳送到所選的 Ethereum 網路。";

"Are you sure you want to archive this planet? Archived planets will not be auto updated. You can later unarchive it from settings." = "確定要封存這個 Planet 嗎？封存的 Planet 不會自動更新。之後可以在「設定」中取消封存。";

"Planet lets you build and host your website on your Mac without requiring a centralized service." = "Planet 可讓你直接在 Mac 上建置和託管網站，不需要中心化服務。";

"You can also use Planet to follow the content creators you like." = "你也可以用 Planet 關注喜歡的內容創作者。";

"The big difference is that there is no middle layer between you and the content creators you follow." = "最大的區別是，你和關注的內容創作者之間沒有中間層。";

"You will receive the latest updates in a peer-to-peer manner." = "你會以點對點方式收到最新更新。";

"The slug is the part of the URL that identifies the article. It should be unique and contain only lowercased letters, numbers, and hyphens." = "Slug 是 URL 中用來識別文章的部分。它必須是唯一值，且只能包含小寫字母、數字和連字號。";

"If you want this article to redirect to an external link, enter the URL here." = "如果希望這篇文章重新導向到外部連結，請在這裡輸入 URL。";

"This domain will be used in places that need a domain prefix, like for RSS or Podcast feeds." = "此網域會用在需要網域前置字串的位置，例如 RSS 或 Podcast Feed。";

"Are you sure you want to archive this planet? Archived planets will not be auto published. You can later unarchive it from settings." = "確定要封存這個 Planet 嗎？封存的 Planet 不會自動發佈。之後可以在「設定」中取消封存。";

"Please input an integer for sorting, entries with smaller numbers will be ranked first." = "請輸入整數作為排序值，數字較小的項目會排在前面。";

"Articles of the Page type are not listed on the blog index page, nor are they included in the RSS feed." = "「頁面」類型的文章不會列在部落格索引頁，也不會包含在 RSS Feed 中。";

"Are you sure you want to delete this article? This action will remove it from your feed. However, if the article is still available on the source, it will reappear in your feed the next time you refresh it." = "確定要刪除這篇文章嗎？此操作會將它從你的摘要中移除。不過，如果原始來源仍可取用，下次重新整理時它會再次出現。";


